'''Cabaayad''' ({{lang-en|cloak}}; {{lang-ar|عباية}}) sidoo kale loo yaqaano '''Cabaaya''', waa maro dabacsan oo ka samaysan [[dun]], ama [[cudbi]], ama [[harag]] kaasi oo la tolay looguna tallo-galay in dumarku xidhaan si u asturaan xubnaha jidhkooda. Cabaayadu waxay ka mid tahay [[dhar|dharka khaaska u ah dumarka]]. Sidoo kale waxaa cabaayada aad caan uga yahay [[Islaam|Dunida Islaamka]] taasi oo dumarku u xidhaas astaan diin ahaaneed. Meelaha qaar sida [[Bariga Dhexe|Gobolka Bariga Dhexe]] iyo deegaanada kale ee [[Carab|Dadka Carabta]] ah waxaa caan ka ah xidhashada xijaabka oo loo isticmaalo dhar ahaan. Dharka waxaa laga sameeyaa dun ka timaada haraga [[xoolo|xoolaha]], [[xayawaan]]ka iyo [[cudbi]]ga iyo noocyo aartifishal ah. Marka dharka la samaynayo waxa la isticmaalaa habab badan oo kala duwan, waxaa ugu caansan tolida, mareegida, iyo isku xidhxidhka dunta.<ref>Barber, Elizabeth Wayland (1994). ''Women's Work. The first 20,000 Years'', p.135.Norton & Company, New York. {{ISBN|0-393-31348-4}}</ref> 
==Hordhac==
Cabaayadu waa shey dhar ah taasi oo laga tollo [[dun]] isla markaana aad looga istimaalo deegaanda ku dhaqan yihiin [[Muslim]]iintu halkaasi ooy ka tahay dhar ka mid ah dhaqanka dadka. Xijaabka waxaa maanta laga xidhaa meelo badan oo caalamka ah kuwaasi waxaa ka mid ah wadano badan oo [[Afrika]]an ah iyo wadano reer Galbeed ah.<ref>{{cite book|author=J. R. Bartlett|title=The First and Second Books of the Maccabees|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=uj44AAAAIAAJ&pg=PA246|accessdate=17 April 2013|date=19 July 1973|publisher=CUP Archive|isbn=978-0-521-09749-9|page=246|quote="traditional Jewish head-dress was either something like the Arab's ''Keffiyeh'' (a cotton square folded and wound around a head) or like a turban or stocking cap"}}</ref>
==Dharka==
'''[[Dhar]]ka''' ({{lang-en|Textile ama Cloth}}; {{lang-ar|نسيج (قماش)}}) waa shay dabacsan oo ka samaysan [[dun]] la xardhay. Dharka waxaa laga sameeyaa dun ka timaada haraga [[xoolo|xoolaha]], [[xayawaan]]ka iyo [[cudbi]]ga iyo noocyo aartifishal ah.<ref>C. Willett and Phillis Cunnington, ''The History of Underclothes'', Dover Publications Inc., New York 1992. {{ISBN|0-486-27124-2}} pp. 23–25</ref> Marka dharka la samaynayo waxa la isticmaalaa habab badan oo kala duwan, waxaa ugu caansan tolida, mareegida, iyo isku xidhxidhka dunta. God ku yaala galbeedka wadanka Joorjiya ee bariga [[Yurub]] ayaa waxa laga helay qidcad harag oo lagu wado in dhar ahaan loo isticmaali jirey wakhti hada laga joogo 34,000 oo sano. Dharka guud ahaan waxaa la isku yidhaahdaa '''Hu<nowiki>'</nowiki>'''; kaasi oo u kala baxa noocyo badan. Kugu ugu muhiimsan ee dadku isticmaalaan maalin kasta waxaa ka mid ah: [[surwaal]]ka, [[shaadh]]ka, [[dirac]]a, [[shalmad]]a, [[goono (dhar)|goonada]], [[koodh (dhar)|koodhka]], [[kabbo|kabaha]] iyo kuwo kale oo badan.<ref>''"[[surwaal]]ka, [[shaadh]]ka, [[dirac]]a, [[shalmad]]a, [[goono (dhar)|goonada]], [[koodh (dhar)|koodhka]], [[kabbo|kabaha]]"''</ref><ref>C. Willett and Phillis Cunnington, ''The History of Underclothes'', Dover Publications Inc., New York 1992. {{ISBN|0-486-27124-2}} pp. 54</ref>
